br />\n美斯每年薪金為1.7億。<br />\n<br />\n咁美斯係幫球會賺錢定蝕錢？？？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:48:30.000Z","msg":"老細請你搵番自己份人工就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我樓下送外賣果D一粒鍾都幫老細搵幾十倍人工啦<br />\n<br />\n相對其他球員，佢係貴就貴架啦，如果唔係都唔會畀人攞嚟講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攞呢個POINT黎兜，根本錯撚左焦點。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢件事，我作為美斯迷根本唔洗兜<br />\n問題錯不在美斯，係錯在個老闆當初肯開呢個價，而自己冇計好條數，風險就要佢自己承擔架啦。<br />\n關美斯咩事？佢都係履行合約。<br />\n<br />\n你份合約要去踢波啫，如果美斯冇盡力踢就係佢問題。就可以怪佢<br />\n財赤就唔關美斯事。<br />\n<br />\n至於願唔願意減薪就要雙方共識。你可以話佢唔願意減薪搞衰球會，但唔可以睇完佢份約，話美斯有問題。<br />\n<br />\n支持美斯，概念要分清，唔係會俾人笑柒。"},{"pid":"eafbfeee6e5151e1898e18501ac50310bc4a16f5","tid":2391253,"uid":75406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca2e970cad68b882db81d9dcdedda7174f905dda","tid":2391253,"uid":47783,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"幫佢地答<br />\n唔出美斯糧垃圾巴可以淨賺最少3億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以美斯正仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17bf58b37a382785d833a056d5507e19ca344dfb","tid":2391253,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8af30f278b0c52869919b875e455b2bb9c9154c","tid":2391253,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88bb0992d2c8fa34c5d33f034f3569a91510d02c","tid":2391253,"uid":47783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"唔過2頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"推到兩頁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"唔會過"},{"pid":"26028c015bcb17b438bf9f24c75bfebaffd2b9d2","tid":2391253,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17bf58b37a382785d833a056d5507e19ca344dfb","tid":2391253,"uid":67225,"like":0,"d